---
title: Garlic Butter Roasted Chicken with Bacon, Brussels Sprouts & Baby Broccoli Salad
description: We’re putting on a spread tonight and there’s a little something for everyone. From the glowing golden chicken roasted in a
herb and garlic butter to the veggies with hidden bits of bacon and Brussel sprouts for the touch of green we love. If anyone
at the table has a sweet tooth then the pecans dotted through the baby broccoli salad with creamy feta with surely satisfy.
